      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46560,46948</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほぇあ～～、まったく、まったく。
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;は、気立てのええ娘っ子だ～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haaa! Good grief! &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; could so naturally be my daughter!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へん、おまえは&lt;Mel&gt;の
一面しか見てねーんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh! You've only seen what &lt;Mel&gt;'s like from the outside.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだぁ？　おめぇ、嫉妬してるだか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What? Do you mean to say you know her deep secrets then?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつは、オレがせっかくうまく作った
カレーに意地悪でマシュマロ入れたり……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That girl almost tried to kill me by putting rotten mushrooms in that my curry on purpose!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うそ、こけぇ！
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;が、そっだらことするわけねぇ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop lying, brat! &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; would never do that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>寝てる間にオレの顔に落書きしたり、
庭にこっそり落とし穴掘ったり</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When I was sleeping, she grabbed me by the face. She sneaked me to the garden dropped me to a hole</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>家の壁に、こっそり『&lt;Mel&gt;参上』とか書いたり、
隠れたところで悪行三昧だぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>and wrote "&lt;Mel&gt; was here!" After that she pretended to be completely innocent! (I am extremely thrown off with this...)</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ウソ言わないでよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop lying!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はん！　やーっぱり、あのチビ助のウソだったか。
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;がそんな意地悪しないって、わかってただよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah! I knew that brat was just spouting lies! I knew &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; wasn't bad at all!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大体、カレーにマシュマロ入れるなんて、
ウソをつくにも、程度が低過ぎるっつー話だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He obviously was lying about all the deal with the Mushrooms in the Curry! He just wanted all the attention for himself with his blabbering!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だ、だって……
甘い方が好きなんだもん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>S-still I love sweet things.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47044</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_015_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まっさっか。そったらことが……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't tell me that...So y-you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
